        "name": "Brasil"
      },
      "serviceType": ["Holding Patrimonial", "Holding Familiar", "Holding Imobiliária", "Planejamento Sucessório", "Proteção Patrimonial"]
    },
    {
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "@id": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/constituicao-de-holding-patrimonial-e-familiar/",
      "url": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/constituicao-de-holding-patrimonial-e-familiar/",
      "name": "Constituição de Holding Patrimonial e Familiar | AM Cabral",
      "description": "Constitua sua holding patrimonial ou familiar. Reduza IR sobre aluguel de 27,5% para 8,4%, proteja bens e planeje a sucessão. 30 anos de experiência.",
      "inLanguage": "pt-BR",
      "dateModified": "2026-04-06",
      "isPartOf": { "@id": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/#website" },
      "breadcrumb": { "@id": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/constituicao-de-holding-patrimonial-e-familiar/#breadcrumb" }
    },
    {
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "@id": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/constituicao-de-holding-patrimonial-e-familiar/#breadcrumb",
      "itemListElement": [
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Serviços", "item": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/servicos" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Holding Patrimonial e Familiar", "item": "https://amcabralblindagem.com.br/constituicao-de-holding-patrimonial-e-familiar/" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "O que é holding patrimonial?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "A holding patrimonial é uma empresa constituída exclusivamente para administrar bens — imóveis, investimentos, veículos, participações societárias. Os bens deixam de estar no CPF do dono e passam para o CNPJ da holding, o que reduz a tributação sobre aluguéis de 27,5% para aproximadamente 8,4% e facilita a sucessão familiar sem inventário judicial."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Holding é só para quem é rico?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Não. A holding patrimonial faz sentido para qualquer empresário com patrimônio a partir de R$ 1 milhão ou que receba aluguéis acima de R$ 5 mil/mês. A partir desse patamar, a economia tributária e a proteção patrimonial já compensam os custos de constituição e manutenção da holding."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Qual a diferença entre holding e testamento?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "O testamento define quem herda, mas os bens ainda passam por inventário judicial — processo caro (custas + ITCMD + honorários podem chegar a 15-20% do patrimônio) e demorado (2 a 5 anos). A holding permite transferir quotas em vida, com cláusulas de usufruto, inalienabilidade e reversão, evitando o inventário e garantindo que o patrimônio chegue aos herdeiros de forma rápida e com menor custo tributário."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Quanto custa constituir uma holding?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "O custo de constituição varia de R$ 8.000 a R$ 25.000, dependendo da quantidade de bens, complexidade da estrutura societária e estado de registro. Inclui honorários contábeis, taxas de registro na Junta Comercial, custos de cartório e ITBI. A manutenção mensal (contabilidade da holding) varia de R$ 500 a R$ 2.000. Em geral, a economia tributária paga o investimento em 6 a 12 meses."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Como a reforma tributária afeta holdings?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "A reforma tributária de 2025 trouxe mudanças importantes: (1) possibilidade de tributação de dividendos a partir de 2026, o que torna urgente estruturar holdings agora; (2) reavaliação de imóveis com alíquota reduzida até 2027 — janela única para atualizar valor dos bens; (3) o CIB (Cadastro Imobiliário Brasileiro) vai cruzar dados de aluguel com a Receita. Quem não estruturar agora pode perder essas janelas de oportunidade."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Preciso de advogado ou contadora para holding?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Idealmente, os dois trabalham juntos. A contadora cuida da estrutura tributária — regime de tributação, apuração de impostos, obrigações acessórias e contabilidade mensal. O advogado cuida do contrato social, cláusulas de proteção e aspectos jurídicos da sucessão. Na AM Cabral, trabalhamos em parceria com escritórios de advocacia especializados para entregar uma solução completa."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
</script>

<style>
/* === SR-ONLY === */
.sr-only {
  position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: -1px;
  overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,0,0); white-space: nowrap; border: 0;
}

/* === SKIP LINK === */
.skip-link {
  position: absolute; top: -40px; left: 0; background: var(--accent);
  color: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; z-index: 99999; font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 14px; transition: top .2s;
}
.skip-link:focus { top: 0; }

/* === VARIABLES === */
:root {
  --ink: #060E1A;
  --ink2: #0A1628;
  --paper: #F1F5F9;
  --paper2: #E2E8F0;
  --paper3: #CBD5E1;
  --dim: #94A3B8;
  --faint: #CBD5E1;
  --accent: #3B82F6;
  --accent2: #60A5FA;
  --accent-bg: rgba(59,130,246,.08);
  --gold: #C9A84C;
  --serif: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
  --sans: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  --z0: #060E1A;
  --z1: #0A1628;
  --z2: #0F2137;
  --z3: #132D4A;
  --z4: #1A3A5C;
  --spring: cubic-bezier(.16, 1, .3, 1);
  --border-z1: rgba(255,255,255,.055);
  --border-z2: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  --border-z3: rgba(255,255,255,.11);
  --toplight: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  --toplight-strong: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.1);
  --zi-nav: 300;
  --zi-bar: 301;
  --zi-prog: 999;
  --r-card: 12px;
  --r-pill: 999px;
  --r-subtle: 4px;
  --radius: 16px;
  --radius-sm: 8px;
  --glow-accent: rgba(59,130,246,.14);
  --glow-accent-edge: rgba(96,165,250,.07);
  --glow-gold: rgba(201,168,76,.06);
  --glow-warn: rgba(239,68,68,.08);
  --sec-pad: clamp(100px, 12vw, 160px);
  --sp-2: 8px; --sp-3: 12px; --sp-4: 16px; --sp-6: 24px; --sp-8: 32px;
  --t-fast: 150ms; --t-normal: 250ms; --t-slow: 400ms; --t-slower: 750ms;
  --shadow-2: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.25), 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
  --shadow-3: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.3), 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
}

/* === RESET === */
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

/* === GLOBAL === */
body {
  background: var(--z0); color: var(--paper); font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -.008em; line-height: 1.75;
  overflow-x: hidden; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
*:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--accent2); outline-offset: 2px; }

/* === UTILITIES === */
.container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px); }

/* Reveal animations */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px);
  transition: opacity .8s var(--spring), transform .8s var(--spring);
  will-change: opacity, transform;
}
.reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; will-change: auto; }
.reveal-left {
  opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-40px);
  transition: opacity .8s var(--spring), transform .8s var(--spring);
}
.reveal-left.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
.reveal-right {
  opacity: 0; transform: translateX(40px);
  transition: opacity .8s var(--spring), transform .8s var(--spring);
}
.reveal-right.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
.reveal-scale {
  opacity: 0; transform: scale(.85);
  transition: opacity .7s var(--spring), transform .7s var(--spring);
}
.reveal-scale.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

/* Stagger delays */
.d1 { transition-delay: .08s; }
.d2 { transition-delay: .16s; }
.d3 { transition-delay: .24s; }
.d4 { transition-delay: .32s; }
.d5 { transition-delay: .40s; }
.d6 { transition-delay: .48s; }

/* Noise overlay */
.noise { position: relative; }
.noise::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.85' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='.045'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size: 200px 200px; mix-blend-mode: screen; opacity: .5;
  transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
}
.noise > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

/* === READING PROGRESS BAR === */
.reading-prog {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--accent2) 50%, var(--accent) 100%);
  z-index: var(--zi-prog); width: 0%; pointer-events: none;
  will-change: width; transition: width .1s linear;
}

/* === SECTION TYPOGRAPHY === */
.sec-label {
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .15em;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--dim);
}
.sec-label.lt { color: var(--accent2); }
.sec-label.gold { color: var(--gold); }
.sec-h {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 52px);
  line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -.02em; color: var(--paper); text-wrap: balance;
}
.sec-h em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent2); }
.sec-h .gold { color: var(--gold); }
.sec-desc {
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 18, 'wght' 350;
  line-height: 1.8; max-width: 640px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); text-wrap: pretty;
}

/* === NAV === */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: var(--zi-nav);
  height: 62px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 40px; background: transparent; backdrop-filter: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: top .3s, background .3s, border-color .3s, backdrop-filter .3s;
  will-change: background, backdrop-filter;
}
nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(6,14,26,.9); backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(180%);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(180%);
  border-bottom-color: rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  box-shadow: var(--toplight), 0 1px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
}
.logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: .05em; color: var(--paper); transition: opacity .2s; }
.logo:hover { opacity: .6; }
.nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; align-items: center; }
.nav-btn {
  background: none; border: none; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); padding: 8px 14px; cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; transition: color .2s; white-space: nowrap;
}
.nav-btn:hover { color: var(--paper); }
.nav-btn.active { color: var(--paper); }
.nav-r { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.nav-cta {
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); padding: 10px 24px; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--sans); transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
}
.nav-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(241,245,249,.15); }
.hamburger { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px; }
.hamburger span { display: block; width: 22px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--paper); transition: transform .3s, opacity .3s; }

/* === MOBILE MENU === */
.mob-overlay {
  position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,.6); z-index: 298;
  opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity .3s;
}
.mob-overlay.open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
.mob-menu {
  position: fixed; top: 0; right: 0; width: 280px; height: 100%;
  background: var(--z1); border-left: 1px solid var(--border-z2); z-index: 299;
  transform: translateX(100%); transition: transform .4s var(--spring);
  padding: 80px 24px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
}
.mob-menu.open { transform: translateX(0); }
.mob-menu a {
  display: block; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
  padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-z1); transition: color .2s;
}
.mob-menu a:hover { color: var(--paper); }
.mob-menu-cta {
  margin-top: auto; display: block; text-align: center;
  background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 14px 24px;
}

/* === HERO === */
.hero {
  background: var(--z1); padding: clamp(110px, 14vw, 160px) 0 clamp(80px, 10vw, 120px);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-glow {
  position: absolute; top: -20%; right: -10%; width: 700px; height: 700px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 70% 20%, rgba(201,168,76,.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-glow-2 {
  position: absolute; bottom: -10%; left: -5%; width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--glow-accent) 0%, transparent 65%);
  pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
}
.hero-kicker {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(201,168,76,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.18);
  border-radius: var(--r-pill); padding: 4px 14px 4px 10px;
  color: var(--gold); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 28px;
  opacity: 0; animation: up .6s .1s var(--spring) forwards;
}
.hero-kicker::before {
  content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold); animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}
.hero-h1 {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 58px); line-height: 1.08;
  letter-spacing: -.028em; text-wrap: balance; max-width: 800px;
  opacity: 0; animation: up .9s .18s var(--spring) forwards;
}
.hero-h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 350; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 18, 'wght' 350;
  line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); max-width: 620px;
  margin: 24px 0 36px; text-wrap: pretty;
  opacity: 0; animation: up .9s .3s var(--spring) forwards;
}
.hero-cta {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: var(--r-pill); border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--sans);
  transition: transform .25s var(--spring), box-shadow .25s;
  opacity: 0; animation: up .9s .42s var(--spring) forwards;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) { .hero-cta { font-size: 15px; padding: 16px 40px; } }
.hero-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(201,168,76,.2); }
.hero-breadcrumb {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
  margin-top: 36px; opacity: 0; animation: up .7s .5s var(--spring) forwards;
}
.hero-breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255,255,255,.35); transition: color .2s; }
.hero-breadcrumb a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); }
.hero-breadcrumb strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); font-weight: 500; }

/* === SECTION BASE === */
section.dark { background: var(--z0); color: var(--paper); }
section.light { background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); }
section.sec-pad { padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 130px) 0; }

/* Light section overrides */
.light .sec-label { color: var(--accent); }
.light .sec-label.lt { color: var(--accent); }
.light .sec-label.gold { color: var(--gold); }
.light .sec-h { color: var(--ink); }
.light .sec-h em { color: var(--accent); }
.light .sec-h .gold { color: var(--gold); }
.light .sec-desc { color: var(--dim); }

/* === PAIN SECTION === */
.pain-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px;
  margin-top: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
}
.pain-card {
  background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--paper2); border-radius: var(--r-card);
  padding: 28px; display: flex; gap: 16px;
  border-left: 3px solid #ef4444;
}
.pain-icon {
  width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(239,68,68,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.12);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.pain-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
.pain-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; line-height: 1.35; }
.pain-desc { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.65; }

/* === HOLDING CARDS (dark) === */
.hold-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px;
  margin-top: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
}
.hold-card {
  background: var(--z2); border: 1px solid var(--border-z2); border-radius: var(--r-card);
  padding: 28px 24px; box-shadow: var(--toplight);
  transition: transform var(--t-slow) var(--spring), border-color var(--t-slow), box-shadow var(--t-slow);
}
.hold-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  border-color: rgba(201,168,76,.3);
  box-shadow: var(--toplight), 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
}
.hold-icon {
  width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(201,168,76,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.16);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.hold-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
.hold-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 19px; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.2; }
.hold-desc { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); line-height: 1.7; }

/* === SIMULATION TABLE (light) === */
.sim-wrap {
  margin-top: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
  border-radius: var(--r-card); overflow: hidden;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); background: #fff;
}
.sim-header {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 0;
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--paper2);
}
.sim-header-cell {
  padding: 20px 24px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center;
}
.sim-header-cell:first-child { text-align: left; color: var(--dim); }
.sim-header-cell.pf { color: #dc2626; border-left: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); background: rgba(239,68,68,.03); }
.sim-header-cell.hold { color: var(--gold); border-left: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); background: rgba(201,168,76,.03); }
.sim-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--paper2);
}
.sim-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.sim-cell {
  padding: 16px 24px; font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); text-align: center;
}
.sim-cell:first-child { text-align: left; font-weight: 500; color: var(--dim); }
.sim-cell.pf { border-left: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); background: rgba(239,68,68,.02); }
.sim-cell.hold { border-left: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); background: rgba(201,168,76,.02); }
.sim-cell.pf strong { color: #dc2626; }
.sim-cell.hold strong { color: var(--gold); }
.sim-result {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 0;
  border-top: 2px solid var(--gold); background: rgba(201,168,76,.04);
}
.sim-result-cell {
  padding: 20px 24px; text-align: center;
}
.sim-result-cell:first-child { text-align: left; }
.sim-result-cell.pf { border-left: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); }
.sim-result-cell.hold { border-left: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); }
.sim-result-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); }
.sim-result-num {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
  font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 4px;
}
.sim-caption {
  font-size: 13px; color: var(--dim); text-align: center; padding: 16px 24px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--paper2);
}

/* === TYPES GRID (dark) === */
.types-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;
  margin-top: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
}
.type-card {
  background: var(--z2); border: 1px solid var(--border-z2); border-radius: var(--r-card);
  padding: 32px 24px; box-shadow: var(--toplight);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
  transition: transform var(--t-slow) var(--spring), box-shadow var(--t-slow);
}
.type-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--toplight), 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.3); }
.type-tag {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201,168,76,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.14);
  padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: var(--r-pill); display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.type-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 21px; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; }
.type-desc { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.type-when { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); }
.type-when strong { font-weight: 700; }

/* === PROCESS SECTION === */
.process-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 24px;
  margin-top: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px); text-align: left;
}
.process-step {
  background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid var(--paper2); border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 28px 24px; position: relative;
}
.process-num {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 36px; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--gold); opacity: .4; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.process-title {
  font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.process-desc {
  font-size: 14px; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.7;
}

/* === URGENCY SECTION === */
.urgency-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;
  margin-top: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
}
.urgency-card {
  background: var(--z2); border: 1px solid var(--border-z2); border-radius: var(--r-card);
  padding: 28px 24px; box-shadow: var(--toplight);
  border-left: 3px solid #ef4444; position: relative;
}
.urgency-badge {
  position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px;
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: rgba(239,68,68,.12); color: #ef4444; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: var(--r-pill);
}
.urgency-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.35; padding-right: 80px; }
.urgency-desc { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); line-height: 1.7; }

/* === FAQ === */
.faq-list { max-width: 800px; margin: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px) auto 0; text-align: left; }
.faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--paper2); }
.faq-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--paper2); }
.faq-q {
  width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 24px 0; cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px;
  font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink);
  text-align: left; line-height: 1.4; transition: color .2s;
}
.faq-q:hover { color: var(--accent); }
.faq-q svg { flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform .3s var(--spring); color: var(--dim); }
.faq-q[aria-expanded="true"] svg { transform: rotate(45deg); color: var(--accent); }
.faq-a {
  max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height .4s var(--spring), padding .4s;
  padding: 0;
}
.faq-a.open { max-height: 600px; padding: 0 0 24px 0; }
.faq-a-inner { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 350; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--dim); max-width: 680px; }

/* === CTA FINAL === */
.cta-final {background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background: var(--z2); text-align: center; padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 130px) 0;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.cta-final::before {
  content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  pointer-events: none;
}
.cta-final .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.cta-inner { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }
.cta-tag { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,.3); margin-bottom: 20px; }
.cta-h {
  font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);
  letter-spacing: -.025em; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 20px; text-wrap: balance;
}
.cta-h em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
.cta-desc { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); margin-bottom: 36px; text-wrap: pretty; }
.cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.cta-btn-wa {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  background: #25D366; color: #fff; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 16px 40px;
  border-radius: var(--r-pill); border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--sans);
  transition: transform .25s var(--spring), background .2s, box-shadow .25s;
}
.cta-btn-wa:hover { background: #1ebe5d; transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(37,211,102,.25); }
.cta-sub { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(255,255,255,.25); margin-top: 20px; }

/* === INTERNAL LINKS === */
.internal-links {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-top: 24px;
}
.internal-link {
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: var(--r-pill);
  transition: color .2s, border-color .2s;
}
.internal-link:hover { color: var(--accent2); border-color: rgba(96,165,250,.3); }

/* === FOOTER === */
.footer {
  background: #040A14; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); text-align: center;
  padding: 28px 0; font-size: .78rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
}
.footer strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); }

/* === KEYFRAMES === */
@keyframes up {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  50% { opacity: .4; transform: scale(.75); }
}

/* === REDUCED MOTION === */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after { animation-duration: .01ms !important; transition-duration: .01ms !important; }
  .reveal, .reveal-left, .reveal-right, .reveal-scale { opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; }
  .hero-kicker, .hero-h1, .hero-sub, .hero-cta, .hero-breadcrumb { opacity: 1 !important; }
}

/* === RETINA NOISE === */
@media (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2), (min-resolution: 192dpi) {
  .noise::after { background-size: 150px 150px; opacity: .38; }
}

/* === PRINT === */
@media print {
  body { background: #fff; color: #000; }
  nav, .reading-prog, .cta-final, footer { display: none !important; }
}

/* === RESPONSIVE: TABLET (960px) === */
@media (max-width: 960px) {
  nav { padding: 0 20px; }
  .nav-links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
  .hamburger { display: flex; }
  nav { top: 0 !important; }
  :root { --sec-pad: clamp(64px, 10vw, 100px); }
  .pain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hold-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .sim-header, .sim-row, .sim-result { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
  .types-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .process-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .urgency-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .faq-list { max-width: 100%; }
  .cta-btns { justify-content: center; }
}

/* === RESPONSIVE: MOBILE (480px) === */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .hero-h1 { font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.08; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .sec-h { font-size: clamp(24px, 6.5vw, 32px); }
  .hold-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .sim-header, .sim-row, .sim-result { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .sim-header-cell { border-left: none !important; border-top: 1px solid var(--paper2); }
  .sim-header-cell:first-child { border-top: none; }
  .sim-cell { border-left: none !important; border-top: 1px solid var(--paper2); }
  .sim-cell:first-child { border-top: none; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .sim-result-cell { border-left: none !important; }
  .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .cta-btns { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
  .cta-btn-wa { justify-content: center; }
  .internal-links { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
}

/* === MARQUEES === */
.mq-cred{display:flex;gap:36px;animation:mqc 28s linear infinite;width:max-content}
.mq-cred:hover{animation-play-state:paused}
@keyframes mqc{0%{transform:translateX(0)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
.mqi{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);white-space:nowrap}
.mqd{width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#3B82F6;opacity:.5}
.mq-gold{display:flex;gap:36px;animation:mqg 32s linear infinite;width:max-content}
.mq-gold:hover{animation-play-state:paused}
@keyframes mqg{0%{transform:translateX(0)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
.mqgi{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em;color:#060E1A;white-space:nowrap}
.mqgd{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#060E1A;opacity:.2}

/* Cross-link cards */
.xlink-card{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;transition:border-color .25s,box-shadow .25s,transform .25s;color:inherit}
.xlink-card:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.06);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.xlink-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#060E1A;flex:1}
.xlink-desc{font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;flex:2}
.xlink-arrow{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
@media(max-width:768px){.xlink-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr!important}.xlink-desc{display:none}}

        /* === NEW SITE HEADER & FOOTER === */
        .site-header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15, 20, 25, 0.95), rgba(15, 20, 25, 0.8));
            z-index: 100;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }

        .site-nav {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 48px;
        }

        .nav-logo {
            font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            list-style: none;
            flex: 1;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-item {
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-item > a {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #A8B5C6;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            display: block;
        }

        .nav-item > a:hover {
            color: #C4A574;
        }

        .nav-trigger {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #A8B5C6;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .nav-trigger:hover {
            color: #C4A574;
        }

        .nav-arrow {
            font-size: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        .nav-item.is-open .nav-arrow {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
        }

        .nav-dropdown {
            position: absolute;
            top: calc(100% + 12px);
            left: 0;
            background: #1A2535;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 4px;
            min-width: 240px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            transition: opacity 0.25s, transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .nav-item.has-dropdown:hover .nav-dropdown,
        .nav-item.has-dropdown:focus-within .nav-dropdown {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .nav-dropdown a {
            display: block;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #A8B5C6;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-dropdown a:hover {
            color: #C4A574;
        }

        .dropdown-all {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            margin-top: 4px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            color: #C4A574 !important;
        }

        .nav-cta {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            background: #C4A574;
            color: #0F1419;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 4px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .nav-cta:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(196, 165, 116, 0.2);
        }

        .nav-hamburger {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 5px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .nav-hamburger span {
            width: 20px;
            height: 2px;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .mobile-nav {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: var(--dark-hero);
      z-index: 99;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 80px 24px 24px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s;
        }

        .mobile-nav.is-open {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
      pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .mobile-nav-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 24px;
            right: 24px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-size: 28px;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 4px;
        }

        .mobile-nav a {
            padding: 12px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #A8B5C6;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        }

        .mobile-nav a:hover {
            color: #C4A574;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .nav-cta {
                display: none;
            }

            .nav-hamburger {
                display: flex;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .site-nav {
                padding: 0 16px;
                gap: 24px;
            }

            .nav-logo {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }

        /* === FOOTER === */
        .site-footer {
            background: #0F1419;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            padding: 72px 0 32px;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .footer-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 56px;
        }

        .footer-col {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .footer-heading {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #C4A574;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer-col ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .footer-col a {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #A8B5C6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .footer-col a:hover {
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .footer-brand {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            padding: 32px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .footer-cta {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            background: #C4A574;
            color: #0F1419;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }

        .footer-cta:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(196, 165, 116, 0.2);
        }

        .footer-legal {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding-top: 24px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .footer-legal p,
        .footer-legal-links a {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        .footer-legal-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .footer-legal-links a:hover {
            color: #C4A574;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .footer-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 32px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .site-footer {
                padding: 48px 0 24px;
            }

            .footer-inner {
                padding: 0 16px;
            }

            .footer-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 24px;
            }

